What you need to know:

Suarez struck in the 20th minute with a superb header from Yannick Carrasco's cross to move Diego Simeone's Atletico up to 35 points, two ahead of local rivals MadridUruguay forward Suarez's eighth goal of the season was a good as it got for Atletico, who despite fielding a strong line-up did not impress in a match of little incident at the Wanda MetropolitanoElche then got a spot-kick of their own five minutes into the second half when Dani Carvajal was caught tearing at Antonio Barragan's shirt, with Fidel stepping up to stroke home the leveller